      • calcAverageErrors

        public double[][][] calcAverageErrors(RowData data,
                                      ClusModel model,
                                      ClusStatManager mgr)
                               throws ClusException,
                                      java.lang.InterruptedException
        Calculates values of all error measures.
        Returns:
        [[listOfResultsForErr1, [sign1]], [listOfResultsForErr2, [sign2]], ...],
        where signI = errorI.shouldBeLow() ? -1.0 : 1.0, and listOfResultsForErr always contains the overall Err error in the position 0, and possibly also per target calculations for Err in the positions i > 0.
        Throws:
        ClusException
        java.lang.InterruptedException
